    <entry>
      <title>总结主题美化</title>
      <link href="2021/03/26/20210326-%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/"/>
      <url>2021/03/26/20210326-%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li><a href="#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80">前言</a></li><li><a href="#%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE">主题配置</a><ul><li><a href="#%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2">主题颜色</a></li><li><a href="#%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98">主页面标题</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%AF%BC%E8%88%AA%E6%A0%8F">导航栏</a></li><li><a href="#%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C">滚动效果</a></li><li><a href="#%E9%A1%B5%E8%84%9A">页脚</a></li><li><a href="#%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF">主题背景</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="#%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD">增加功能</a><ul><li><a href="#%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E5%A2%99">照片墙</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE">地图</a><ul><li><a href="#%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6api">百度API</a></li><li><a href="#pyecharts">pyecharts</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="#%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD">点击下载</a></li><li><a href="#%E9%9F%B3%E9%A2%91%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91">音频视频</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86">博客加密</a></li></ul></li></ul><h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>&emsp;&emsp;本主题是Butterfly，安装教程参考<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/21cfbf15/">Butterfly 安裝文檔(一) 快速開始</a>。需要说明教程里“把主題文件夾中的 _config.yml 複製到 Hexo 根目錄裏，同時重新命名為 _config.butterfly.yml。”我没有做。<br>&emsp;&emsp;我用来储存博客的文件夹是Hexo Blog。</p><h1 id="主题配置"><a href="#主题配置" class="headerlink" title="主题配置"></a>主题配置</h1><h2 id="主题颜色"><a href="#主题颜色" class="headerlink" title="主题颜色"></a>主题颜色</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;颜色的修改都在Hexo Blog\themes\butterfly_config.yml中，Theme color for customize栏目里。取消下面三行代码的注释，并修改main的颜色，这个颜色是浅灰色。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme_color:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  main: &quot;#C4C4C4&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="主页面标题"><a href="#主页面标题" class="headerlink" title="主页面标题"></a>主页面标题</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;标题是主页面图片中间的内容，修改内容在Hexo Blog_config.yml中，Site栏目里的title。<br>&emsp;&emsp;修改标题字体的大小，在Hexo Blog\themes\butterfly\source\css_layout\head.styl里，site-title栏目里，修改为5em。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">+minWidth768()</span><br><span class="line">  font-size: 5em</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;主页面可以设置有打字效果的副标题，并调用三方API显示每日一句。修改在Hexo Blog\themes\butterfly_config.yml里，修改代码如下。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">subtitle:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  effect: true</span><br><span class="line">  loop: false</span><br><span class="line">  source: 4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="导航栏"><a href="#导航栏" class="headerlink" title="导航栏"></a>导航栏</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;导航栏内容的增加参考<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/4aa8abbe/">Butterfly 安裝文檔(三) 主題配置-1</a>，我做的更改是去掉了icon的显示，注意<code>Archives: /archives/</code>表示的意思是Archives将会显示在网页的导航栏里，archives是它的文件夹名称，在Hexo Blog\source里。<br>&emsp;&emsp;修改导航栏的字体大小，在Hexo Blog\themes\butterfly\source\css_layout\head.styl里，nav栏目里，修改为1.2em。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#nav</span><br><span class="line">  position: absolute</span><br><span class="line">  top: 0</span><br><span class="line">  z-index: 90</span><br><span class="line">  display: flex</span><br><span class="line">  flex-wrap: wrap</span><br><span class="line">  align-items: center</span><br><span class="line">  padding: 0 36px</span><br><span class="line">  width: 100%</span><br><span class="line">  height: 60px</span><br><span class="line">  font-size: 1.2em</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;下拉菜单本来有一个箭头，鼠标放上面箭头会旋转，我觉得太花。于是删除箭头。修改在Hexo Blog\themes\butterfly\layout\includes\header\menu_item.pug里，menus_item栏目里。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.menus_item</span><br><span class="line">  a.site-page(href&#x3D;&#39;javascript:void(0);&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">    if label.split(&#39;||&#39;)[1]</span><br><span class="line">      i.fa-fw(class&#x3D;trim(label.split(&#39;||&#39;)[1]))</span><br><span class="line">    span&#x3D;&#39; &#39;+ trim(label.split(&#39;||&#39;)[0])</span><br><span class="line">    i.fas.fa-chevron-down.expand(class&#x3D;sidebarChildHide)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;删除其中<code>i.fas.fa-chevron-down.expand(class=sidebarChildHide)</code>一行代码即可。<br>&emsp;&emsp;导航栏左边是副标题，本来想把副标题改的大一点，但是副标题是跟导航栏同步变大，导致导航栏被隐藏了。因此暂时把左侧的副标题不显示。修改在Hexo Blog\themes\butterfly\source\css_layout\head.styl里，site-name栏目里，改为0.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#site-name</span><br><span class="line">  text-shadow: .1rem .1rem .2rem rgba($dark-black, .15)</span><br><span class="line">  font-size: 0em</span><br><span class="line">  cursor: pointer</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="滚动效果"><a href="#滚动效果" class="headerlink" title="滚动效果"></a>滚动效果</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;滚动效果是一个向下的箭头居于背景图片下方，不喜欢它的上下跳动，所以删除该效果。修改在Hexo Blog\themes\butterfly\source\css_layout\head.styl里，scroll-down-effects栏目里，修改图标大小为0.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.scroll-down-effects</span><br><span class="line">  position: relative</span><br><span class="line">  width: 100%</span><br><span class="line">  color: var(--light-grey)</span><br><span class="line">  font-size: 0px</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="页脚"><a href="#页脚" class="headerlink" title="页脚"></a>页脚</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;页脚显示的内容在Hexo Blog\themes\butterfly\layout\includes\footer.pug中，删除以下一段代码。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    if theme.footer.copyright</span><br><span class="line">.framework-info</span><br><span class="line">  span&#x3D; _p(&#39;footer.framework&#39;) + &#39; &#39;</span><br><span class="line">  a(href&#x3D;&#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;hexo.io&#39;)&#x3D; &#39;Hexo&#39;</span><br><span class="line">  span.footer-separator |</span><br><span class="line">  span&#x3D; _p(&#39;footer.theme&#39;) + &#39; &#39;</span><br><span class="line">  a(href&#x3D;&#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;jerryc127&#x2F;hexo-theme-butterfly&#39;)&#x3D; &#39;Butterfly&#39;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="主题背景"><a href="#主题背景" class="headerlink" title="主题背景"></a>主题背景</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;主题背景图片修改在Hexo Blog\themes\butterfly_config.yml里，Image栏目里，注意这里能修改的是默认主题背景<code>The banner image of home page</code>，archive页面背景，子标签页面背景，子分类页面背景。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">index_img: &#x2F;img&#x2F;pic_1.jpg</span><br><span class="line">default_top_img: &#x2F;img&#x2F;pic_1.jpg</span><br><span class="line">archive_img: &#x2F;img&#x2F;pic_2.jpg</span><br><span class="line">tag_img: &#x2F;img&#x2F;pic_5.jpg</span><br><span class="line">tag_per_img: </span><br><span class="line">category_img: &#x2F;img&#x2F;pic_4.jpg</span><br><span class="line">category_per_img: </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;其中的img文件夹位于Hexo Blog\themes\butterfly\source中，可自行更改，但必须以source文件夹为起使索引。<br>&emsp;&emsp;其他页面背景（标签/分类/链接/关于/列表内的照片电影和音乐）都在各自的index.md中设置。例如list里的movie的md文件。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: movie</span><br><span class="line">date: 2018-06-07 22:17:49</span><br><span class="line">updated:</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;movie&quot;</span><br><span class="line">comments:</span><br><span class="line">description:</span><br><span class="line">keywords:</span><br><span class="line">top_img: &#x2F;img_post&#x2F;pic_3.jpg</span><br><span class="line">mathjax:</span><br><span class="line">katex:</span><br><span class="line">aside:</span><br><span class="line">aplayer:</span><br><span class="line">highlight_shrink:</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;其中的img_post文件夹位于Hexo Blog\source中，可自行更改，但必须以source文件夹为起使索引。</p><h1 id="增加功能"><a href="#增加功能" class="headerlink" title="增加功能"></a>增加功能</h1><h2 id="照片墙"><a href="#照片墙" class="headerlink" title="照片墙"></a>照片墙</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;照片页面有两种设计：一是显示图库的缩略图，点击进入图库，出现图库的所有图片；二是直接显示所有图片。都是采用html的写法。<br>&emsp;&emsp;图库的缩略图格式如下。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Photo</span><br><span class="line">date: 2018-06-07 22:17:49</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;photo&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;gallery-group-main&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% galleryGroup &#39;OH MY GIRL&#39; &#39;關於OH MY GIRL的圖片&#39; &#39;&#x2F;gallery&#x2F;ohmygirl&#39; https:&#x2F;&#x2F;i.loli.net&#x2F;2019&#x2F;12&#x2F;25&#x2F;hOqbQ3BIwa6KWpo.jpg %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;其中type可以随意命名，加个s也没问题，改成gallery也没问题。目前不知道其用处。<code>&#39;OH MY GIRL&#39;</code>是图库标题，<code>&#39;關於OH MY GIRL的圖片&#39;</code>是注释，鼠标放在缩略图上才会显示，<code>&#39;/gallery/ohmygirl&#39;</code>是图库的照片的存放位置。位于Hexo Blog\source中。ohmygirl文件夹中也创建一个index.md。修改如下。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Photo</span><br><span class="line">date: 2018-06-07 22:17:49</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;photo&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% gallery %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">![](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;i.loli.net&#x2F;2019&#x2F;12&#x2F;25&#x2F;Fze9jchtnyJXMHN.jpg)</span><br><span class="line">![](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;i.loli.net&#x2F;2019&#x2F;12&#x2F;25&#x2F;ryLVePaqkYm4TEK.jpg)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endgallery %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;其中一个网址是一张照片的链接。</p><h2 id="地图"><a href="#地图" class="headerlink" title="地图"></a>地图</h2><h3 id="百度API"><a href="#百度API" class="headerlink" title="百度API"></a>百度API</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;插入自己进行标注的地图。按照<a href="https://blog.kuretru.com/posts/7a624fc3/">在网页中嵌入百度地图</a>进行，采用的是“另一种 iframe 引用方式，不过此时就不能使用 asset_path 标签了：”这种方式，因为另一种方式运行不成功。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% iframe &#x2F;map.no-render.html 100% 420px %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;其中map.no-render.html存放在Hexo Blog\source中，可自行更改，但必须以source文件夹为起使索引。</p><h3 id="pyecharts"><a href="#pyecharts" class="headerlink" title="pyecharts"></a>pyecharts</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;插入自己进行标注的地图。按照<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/83231415">干货 | 使用pyecharts绘制交互式动态地图</a>进行，按照步骤运行测试代码。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from example.commons import Faker </span><br><span class="line">from pyecharts import options as opts </span><br><span class="line">from pyecharts.charts import Geo </span><br><span class="line">from pyecharts.globals import ChartType, SymbolType</span><br><span class="line">from pyecharts.charts import Map</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">c &#x3D; (</span><br><span class="line">    Geo()</span><br><span class="line">    .add_schema(maptype&#x3D;&quot;world&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">    # .add(&quot;geo&quot;, [list(z) for z in zip([&#39;河南&#39;], [22])])</span><br><span class="line">    .add_coordinate(&#39;TEST&#39;, -1.023194, 7.946527)</span><br><span class="line">    .set_series_opts(label_opts&#x3D;opts.LabelOpts(is_show&#x3D;False))</span><br><span class="line">    .set_global_opts(</span><br><span class="line">        visualmap_opts&#x3D;opts.VisualMapOpts(),</span><br><span class="line">        title_opts&#x3D;opts.TitleOpts(title&#x3D;&quot;Geo-基本示例&quot;),</span><br><span class="line">    )</span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line">c.render()# 输出html格式</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;但是可能报错，根据<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_41228218/article/details/91350196">from example.commons import Faker找不到example解决</a>的提示，安装程序的代码应该如下。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install pyecharts&#x3D;&#x3D;1.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;再次运行就能成功了。接下来考虑使用geo模块标注世界地图，必须输入地点的经纬度数据，尝试过直接把国家名称写到list里，不行。于是自己写了以下代码。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from example.commons import Faker </span><br><span class="line">from pyecharts import options as opts </span><br><span class="line">from pyecharts.charts import Geo </span><br><span class="line">from pyecharts.globals import ChartType, SymbolType</span><br><span class="line">from pyecharts.charts import Map</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">geo &#x3D; Geo()</span><br><span class="line">geo.add_schema(maptype&#x3D;&quot;world&quot;) </span><br><span class="line">geo.add_coordinate(&#39;TEST&#39;, -1.023194, 7.946527) # 输入一个名为TEST的地址</span><br><span class="line">geo.add(&quot;geo&quot;, [list(z) for z in zip([&#39;TEST&#39;], [22])]) # 把TEST放在列表里，加到地图里</span><br><span class="line">geo.set_series_opts(label_opts&#x3D;opts.LabelOpts(is_show&#x3D;False))</span><br><span class="line">geo.set_global_opts(visualmap_opts&#x3D;opts.VisualMapOpts(),title_opts&#x3D;opts.TitleOpts(title&#x3D;&quot;Geo-基本示例&quot;))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">geo.render()# 显示地图</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;运行之后就可以生成一个名为render.html的文件。下面的步骤跟百度API相似，本质都是把一个html展示到网页上。注意修改width为100%。并把render.html改为map.no-render.html放在Hexo Blog\source中，注意map可以改，但是.no-render.html不能改，因为Hexo Blog_config.yml中定义了这种格式为不用渲染的格式。并在相应的md文档中输入如下。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% iframe &#x2F;map.no-render.html 100% 420px %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="点击下载"><a href="#点击下载" class="headerlink" title="点击下载"></a>点击下载</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;只需要在post的md文件中写入<code>[点击下载](https://cloud.tsinghua.edu.cn/f/40c110453aa744579ade/?dl=1 &quot;主题设置文件&quot;)</code>，链接的是文件所在的地址，可以是清华seafile。</p><h2 id="音频视频"><a href="#音频视频" class="headerlink" title="音频视频"></a>音频视频</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;音频和视频的插入在<a href="https://lovelijunyi.gitee.io/posts/743c.html">hexo文章插入多媒体</a>中总结很全。butterfly的官方网站也有。<br>&emsp;&emsp;需要注意的是采用直接插入的方法时，<code>width</code>设置为100%，才能适应手机屏幕的显示。例如插入音频，直接在post的md文件中输入如下。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;iframe frameborder&#x3D;&quot;no&quot; border&#x3D;&quot;0&quot; marginwidth&#x3D;&quot;0&quot; marginheight&#x3D;&quot;0&quot; width&#x3D;100% height&#x3D;86 src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;music.163.com&#x2F;outchain&#x2F;player?type&#x3D;2&amp;id&#x3D;29808783&amp;auto&#x3D;1&amp;height&#x3D;66&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;iframe&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;例如插入视频，直接在post的md文件中输入如下。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;iframe </span><br><span class="line">    width&#x3D;&quot;100%&quot; </span><br><span class="line">    height&#x3D;&quot;450&quot; </span><br><span class="line">    src&#x3D;&#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;player.youku.com&#x2F;embed&#x2F;XNDE5NjYzOTg0OA&#x3D;&#x3D;&#39;</span><br><span class="line">    frameborder&#x3D;&quot;0&quot; </span><br><span class="line">    allowfullscreen&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;iframe&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="博客加密"><a href="#博客加密" class="headerlink" title="博客加密"></a>博客加密</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;按照<a href="https://leehoward.cn/2019/10/26/Hexo%E5%AF%B9%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86/#%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7">Hexo对文章进行加密</a>进行。只测试过对单个博客进行加密。</p>]]></content>
      
      
